e in Joyce's <i>Ulysses</i>), Kedros publishers, 1997</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_translations\">Selected translations</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Aris_Marangopoulos&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: Selected translations\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><i>Note: dates given are of the first publication of the Greek translation</i>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Jonathan_Swift\" title=\"Jonathan Swift\">Swift, Jonathan</a>, <i>\u03a4\u03b1 \u03c4\u03b1\u03be\u03af\u03b4\u03b9\u03b1 \u03c4\u03bf\u03c5 \u0393\u03ba\u03ac\u03bb\u03b9\u03b2\u03b5\u03c1</i> (<i><a href=\"/wiki/Gulliver%27s_Travels\" title=\"Gulliver&#39;s Travels\">Gulliver's Travels</a></i>), 1996</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Daniel_Defoe\" title=\"Daniel Defoe\">Defoe, Daniel</a>, <i>\u03a1\u03bf\u03b2\u03b9\u03bd\u03c3\u03ce\u03bd\u03b1\u03c2 \u039a\u03c1\u03bf\u03cd\u03c3\u03bf\u03c2</i> (<i><a href=\"/wiki/Robinson_Crusoe\" title=\"Robinson Crusoe\">Robinson Crusoe</a></i>),  1997</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/James_Joyce\" title=\"James Joyce\">Joyce, James</a>, <i>\u03a4\u03b6\u03b9\u03ac\u03ba\u03bf\u03bc\u03bf \u03a4\u03b6\u03cc\u03b9\u03c2</i> (<i><a href=\"/wiki/Giacomo_Joyce\" title=\"Giacomo Joyce\">Giacomo Joyce</a></i>),  1994</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Henry_James\" title=\"Henry James\">James, Henry</a>, <i>\u03a0\u03bb\u03b1\u03c4\u03b5\u03af\u03b1 \u039f\u03c5\u03ac\u03c3\u03b9\u03b3\u03ba\u03c4\u03bf\u03bd</i>  (<i><a href=\"/wiki/Washington_Square_(novel)\" title=\"Washington Square (novel)\">Washington Square</a></i>), 1997</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Honor%C3%A9_de_Balzac\" title=\"Honor\u00e9 de Balzac\">Balzac, Honor\u00e9 de</a>, <i>\u03a3\u03b1\u03c1\u03b1\u03b6\u03af\u03bd\u03bf\u03c2</i> (<i><a href=\"/wiki/Sarrasine\" title=\"Sarrasine\">Sarrasine</a></i>), 1999</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Marguerite_Duras\" title=